{"name": "odoo-addon-product-multi-barcode", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-multi-barcode", "version": "16.0.1.0.1.4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Multiple barcodes on products", "upload_time": 1717049761}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fstock--logistics--barcode-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/stock-logistics-barcode\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode/tree/16.0/product_multi_barcode\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/stock-logistics-barcode-16-0/stock-logistics-barcode-16-0-product_multi_barcode\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/stock-logistics-barcode&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Multiple barcodes on products\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:9ef01fd1fe41f2bceb16613c4a7d5ca731849f60e90f640626becbdd4d0511d2\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows you to define multiple barcodes on products.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nA list of barcodes is available for each product with a priority, so a main barcode\ncode is defined.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode/issues/new?body=module:%20product_multi_barcode%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n- Trey\n- Tecnativa\n- QubiQ\n- ADHOC SA\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Guewen Baconnier (Camptocamp)\n\n- Roberto Lizana (Trey)\n\n- Pedro M. Baeza\n\n- Xavier Jimenez (QubiQ)\n\n- H\u00e9ctor Villarreal (Eficent)\n\n- S\u00e9bastien Beau (Akretion)\n\n- Kevin Khao (Akretion)\n\n- Ooops404 \\<<https://ooops404.com>>\n\n  - Ilyas \\<<mailto:irazor147@gmail.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/stock-logistics-barcode](https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode/tree/16.0/product_multi_barcode) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_barcode", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models..product_barcode", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models..product_product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models..product_template", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.tests", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.tests.test_product_multi_barcode", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.tests..test_product_multi_barcode", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_barcode", "documentation": ["\u00a9 2012-2014 Guewen Baconnier (Camptocamp SA)", "\u00a9 2015 Roberto Lizana (Trey)", "\u00a9 2016 Pedro M. Baeza", "\u00a9 2018 Xavier Jimenez (QubiQ)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_barcode.ProductBarcode", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_barcode.ProductBarcode._compute_product_tmpl", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_multi_barcode.models.product_barcode.ProductBarcode._compute_product", "asynchronous": false, "para